{"type": "article", "id": 27030, "title": "磁性 iPhone 架", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-19T07:13:49Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 43, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021524344WFN80lo3fXIY6vH.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>Chris Johnson 为 <a href=\"http://bitemyapple.co/\">BiteMyApple</a> 设计的磁性 iPhone 架 Kiyojo 是一个希望在你因为下厨、锻炼等原因而无法顺利使用手机时解放你双手的小工具。它能够牢牢地吸附在冰箱或是其他金属表面上，所以无论是察看菜谱还是边下厨边和人 FaceTime 你都不用再手忙脚乱了。如果你对 Kiyojo 感兴趣的话，可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/bitemyapple/kiyojo-the-best-magnetic-dock-for-your-iphone-6-6s\">链接</a>参与众筹，售价为 59 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152432NRxhwoSv1U5MdyfV.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.56285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152432t5icKemCRLOokybh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021524338LgcHG5rYRTlZxyt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152433aNiQFDKvgPlhs3O9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}